{
  "stem": "18581.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I wasn't-- I didn't want to leave my father behind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no way I could take my father with me, because the age was very-- the age group was very clear, up to 30 or so.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went with his blessing, but probably with broken heart, I assume.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the same was true about me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went to the forester.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there I worked in the office, mainly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Until [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the Germans surrounded Varenavas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we heard about it, so we immediately ran away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The 24th day of [NON-ENGLISH], which I believe conforms to the 28th of April, 1942.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's when my father was killed together with the rest of the Jews of Varenavas, Dzieveniskes, Kalelishok, and some refugees like ourselves from Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This date has to be checked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, there were-- since it was still a-- a Lithuanian kind of a-- district, maybe the local people were mainly white Russians and Poles, but there were-- there was a Lithuanian element and Lithuanians were in charge.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they needed someone who speaks Lithuanian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I spoke Lithuanian and German and Polish, so I-- all the languages that they needed in the office.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- first of all, not all of them were keen to see the Jews killed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some had remorse.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some were afraid what happened-- what will happen to them after the Russians come back, because in '42, some of them already started to doubt the permanency of the Thousand-Year Reich.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they wanted to-- to say a good word.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And actually, they were simply repeating what they heard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Forester.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard from some people who heard from some people that they had a-- a radio that could pick up BBC shortwaves.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
